'''埃德·里德'''（{{lang-en|Ed Reed}}，{{bd|1978年|9月11日}}），[[美式足球|美式足球]][[游卫|游卫]]，效力于[[国家橄榄球联盟|国家橄榄球联盟]]的[[巴尔的摩乌鸦|巴尔的摩乌鸦]]队。他原先在[[迈阿密大学|迈阿密大学]]打球，2002年选秀中被乌鸦队以第一轮第24顺位选中，此后便一直在乌鸦队中效力。

里德曾八次入选[[明星碗|明星碗]]，被评为2004年[[NFL年度防守球员|NFL年度防守球员]]，还是NFL史上最长截球回攻纪录的保持者（108码）。他被认为是目前在NFL中效力的最具统治力的安全卫之一，被誉为“球场神鹰”（ball hawk）。<ref>{{cite web |last=Wilson |first=Aaron |url=http://ravens.scout.com/2/551522.html |title=Top free safety in the game |work=Scout.com |date=2006-07-31 |accessdate=2008-11-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071018054655/http://ravens.scout.com/2/551522.html |archivedate=2007-10-18 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Sando |first=Mike |url=http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/columns/story?columnist=sando_mike&id=3056627 |title=Five to fear: Manning, Brady, Moss, Smith, Gates |work=Sports.espn.go.com |date=2007-10-07 |accessdate=2008-11-28 |archive-date=2015-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150713041710/http://sports.espn.go.com/nfl/columns/story?columnist=sando_mike&id=3056627 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2005/writers/jeffri_chadiha/08/30/chadiha.safeties/index.html |first=Jeffri |last=Chadiha |title=Top 10 players at the NFL's hottest defensive position |work=Sportsillustrated.cnn.com |date=2005-08-30 |accessdate=2008-11-28 |archive-date=2010-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100305182350/http://sportsillustrated.cnn.com/2005/writers/jeffri_chadiha/08/30/chadiha.safeties/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Borges |first=Ron |url=http://www.bostonherald.com/sports/football/patriots/view.bg?articleid=1047753 |title=Belichick: Reed’s a keeper |publisher=Boston Herald website |date= |accessdate=2008-11-28 |archive-date=2008-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081202154252/http://www.bostonherald.com/sports/football/patriots/view.bg?articleid=1047753 |dead-url=no }}</ref>里德拥有[[遗觉记忆|遗觉记忆]]（eidetic memory），可以将对方球队的动向清晰地记忆在脑中<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/01/AR2006080101243.html?nav=emailpage |title=Reed Is Determined To Outsmart Rivals |work=Washington Post website |date=2006-08-01 |accessdate=2008-11-28 |first=Camille |last=Powell |archive-date=2018-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914022741/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/08/01/AR2006080101243.html?nav=emailpage |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Hensley |first=Jamison |url=http://www.usatoday.com/sports/football/nfl/2005-07-06-sw-spotlight-db_x.htm |title=Spotlight on defensive backs |publisher=USA Today website |date=2005-07-06 |accessdate=2008-11-28 |archive-date=2009-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091010224439/http://www.usatoday.com/sports/football/nfl/2005-07-06-sw-spotlight-db_x.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时他拥有诱使四分卫传出被截球的能力，被认为是联盟中这一能力最强的防守球员。<ref>{{cite web |last=Prisco |first=Pete |url=http://www.sportsline.com/nfl/story/8805736 |title=Secondary deceivers: Reed, Bailey best at sucking in QBs |work=Sportsline.com |date=2005-09-04 |accessdate=2008-11-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081201091509/http://www.sportsline.com/nfl/story/8805736 |archivedate=2008-12-01 }}</ref>

